Tidy is to revolutionize the cleaning service industry by providing
unparalleled convenience, reliability, and excellence through our
innovative mobile application. We are dedicated to simplifying the
process of accessing top-tier cleaning services while prioritizing
customer satisfaction, integrity, and environmental sustainability.
.
Our mission
Individuals and businesses alike face difficulties in locating trustworthy cleaners
who can meet their specific needs and preferences. This can lead to frustration,
wasted time, and dissatisfaction with the cleanliness of their spaces. Moreover,
there may be a lack of efficient platforms connecting cleaners with potential
customers, resulting in missed job opportunities for cleaners.
In many regions, despite the demand for cleaning services, there's a gap between
cleaners seeking work and customers seeking their services. This disconnect can
hinder economic growth and create barriers to employment opportunities within
the cleaning industry.

Our idea aims to revolutionize the cleaning industry
by leveraging technology to connect individuals and
businesses with reliable cleaning services while
simultaneously creating job opportunities for
cleaners.
By streamlining the process through efficient digital
solutions, we envision a world where cleanliness is
more accessible, economic opportunities are
abundant, and communities thrive. We believe in the
transformative power of our vision to enhance lives,
foster economic growth, and create a cleaner, more
prosperous future for all.
Solution
Our innovative platform revolutionizes the cleaning industry,
connecting users with trusted cleaners while creating job
opportunities. By streamlining the process through cutting-edge
technology, we provide convenience, reliability, and economic
empowerment. Our offering transforms lives, fosters growth, and
creates a cleaner, more prosperous world for all

How do you make money?
Our primary revenue stream is generated through a
commission-based model on completed cleaning
transactions facilitated through our platform.
What is your average transaction size?
The average transaction size varies depending on
factors such as the size of the cleaning job, the
frequency of service, and additional services
requested.
How do you acquire new customers?
Customer Acquisition: We employ a multi-faceted
approach to acquire new customers, including:
Digital Marketing, Referral Programs, Strategic,
Partnerships, Social Media Engagement, SEO
